# Backend Rules

## Package Management
```bash
uv add package-name     # add dependency
uv run python script.py # run script
uv run uvicorn app.main:app --reload  # run server
```

## Supabase Query Pattern
```python
from app.database import supabase

# Always .execute() at the end
result = supabase.table("table_name").select("*").eq("field", value).execute()
data = result.data  # list of dicts

# Insert
result = supabase.table("table_name").insert({"field": value}).execute()

# Update
result = supabase.table("table_name").update({"field": value}).eq("id", id).execute()

# Delete
result = supabase.table("table_name").delete().eq("id", id).execute()
```

## Router Pattern
```python
from fastapi import APIRouter, HTTPException
router = APIRouter()

@router.get("/")
async def list_items():
    result = supabase.table("items").select("*").execute()
    return result.data

@router.post("/")
async def create_item(payload: ItemCreate):
    result = supabase.table("items").insert(payload.model_dump()).execute()
    if not result.data:
        raise HTTPException(status_code=400, detail="Creation failed")
    return result.data[0]
```

## Schema Pattern
```python
from pydantic import BaseModel
from typing import Optional
from uuid import UUID
from datetime import datetime, date

class ItemCreate(BaseModel):
    title: str
    priority: int = 3

class ItemResponse(ItemCreate):
    id: UUID
    created_at: datetime
```

## Register Router in main.py
```python
from app.routers import new_router
app.include_router(new_router.router, prefix="/route", tags=["Tag"])
```

## Never
- Never use SQLAlchemy or any ORM
- Never use raw SQL with psycopg2
- Never use pip — always uv
- Never skip HTTPException on errors
